<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Hello Hattie. If you pick it up to read, you will find that this is really more about a man who wanted to find God, was certain he would find answers <a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Hello Hattie. If you pick it up to read, you will find that this is really more about a man who wanted to find God, was certain he would find answers in Japan, and found a mentor who was willing to teach him Taoism. This is a spiritual adventure, full of symbolism and a real life desire to find something beyond ourselves. In the end, he finds God the Father, but its quite an adventure getting there! <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
